summaries.short: The Monster Sitters step in to help Sid and Lucy finish making all their cards for Warm and Fuzzy Day and later show Snugs how to play safely with his baby brother.
summaries.full: Sid and Lucy arrive at Monster Sitters’ HQ to make cards for a Warm and Fuzzy Day party, but can Esme and Roy help them finish all their cards in time? Plus, a monster meltdown’s on deck when Snugs learns that his favorite big-kid games aren’t safe for baby Fuzzy. Will Esme and Roy find a way for the monster siblings to play together?
